metadata.description:
+I'm afraid I'll never find my way out.
Said the girl, unaware that there is no way out.
-You can't get out of here, but you can get used to being here.
Said the voice from the dark. She felt as if she knew the owner of this voice, but she was very confused and couldn't remember anything properly.
+But how?
-Find the light in the dark.


~

Created and rendered in MagicaVoxel
Includes over 25,200,000 cubes
